        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/leoboe/{size}/479_2.png",
        "created_at": "2010-11-17T23:34:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Youre partially right I think.</p>\n<p>The Islands themselves on LBA2 are created from heightmaps which can be displayed as 2d-Images.<br>\nBut all of the Objects like buildings or caves and such are done with Models so thats where real-3d comes along.</p>\n<p>You can see those two types very well if you watch the island from beneath with the available Island-viewer(s)</p>",
