        "cooked": "<p>here is the video that gave me the idea:</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"hDNVNImNI4s\" data-video-title=\"Little Big Adventure 2 Making of/ Behind the scenes FULL ENGLISH SUBS [LBA2- Final Interview]\" data-video-start-time=\"\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hDNVNImNI4s\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-thumbnail\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/uploads/default/original/3X/e/e/ee5b0c231011bf07a6b9758c28d7a07f4938b14d.jpeg\" title=\"Little Big Adventure 2 Making of/ Behind the scenes FULL ENGLISH SUBS [LBA2- Final Interview]\" data-dominant-color=\"6C5F55\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n<p>\ngoto 2:38 to see the map editing<br>\n(should we ask Fred for the editor?)</p>",
